  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2019-07-25",
    "date": "2021-09-13T16:51:00Z",
    "text": "Smoke-Free Schools Act of 2019\n\nThis bill prohibits the use of any tobacco product (e.g., electronic nicotine delivery systems such as e-cigarettes) in an indoor facility that is regularly used for children's services, including health care, day care, early development, education, or library services. Current law prohibits smoking in such facilities."
